{"tid":661862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"2點全露之後　王思佳不認走光取暖謝網友","createTime":"2018-05-12T02:53:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T06:01:38.000Z","uid":173208,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"86ed8fdc38fca1270c25f8683ab288034066a3a9","tid":661862,"uid":173208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T02:53:59.000Z","msg":"王思佳昨（11日）出席第16屆微風之夜，和媽媽布蘭妮站台《死侍2》電影首映會，未料意外走光露2點，經紀人事後稱「有貼胸貼」，搶盡新聞版面，不少網友在她的社群留言關心，王思佳親上火線回覆，表示「我會小心！謝謝你」，強調自己有貼胸貼。<br />\n<br />\n王思佳意外走光不只引起台灣網友熱議，中國網友也十分關心，在她的微博留言提醒她「出席活動以後要更加留心，不要曝光了」，成功釣出王思佳本人回應，她表示：「我會小心！謝謝你！」再次強調自己有貼胸貼，並附和網友留言，認為是新聞太誇大，堅持不認走光一事。（洪彩婷／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://video.eyny.com/index.php?mod=video&amp;vid=3066197&amp;size=480\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvideo.eyny.com%2Findex.php%3Fmod%3Dvideo%26vid%3D3066197%26size%3D480&d=U8lfYkp3pziho3dMdODr2jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=dae8cadd\" target=\"_blank\">https://video.eyny.com/index.php?mod=video&amp;vid=3066197&amp;size=480</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f14400a1abd2eb1aa3c8f48a33b9b8c8c4bed845","tid":661862,"uid":188,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T02:58:05.000Z","msg":"強調自己有貼胸貼<br />\n<br />\n睇哂啦"},{"pid":"ddf1f4a9ac07d56085304acf0a8706eab639566c","tid":661862,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:01:25.000Z","msg":"Lin黎啦"},{"pid":"ed72374d46a0ec01438a70696a04b14afb6339eb","tid":661862,"uid":61257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:03:28.000Z","msg":"好細粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  黑黑地"},{"pid":"1725199841842f90101034a8e435a64bc72d30dc","tid":661862,"uid":4950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-12T03:04:54.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/as